  <description>
    <p>Clash is a rules-based, cross-platform proxy application core program. Clash Verge is a Clash GUI.</p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Full <code>clash</code> config supported, Partial <code>clash premium</code> config supported.</li>
      <li>Profiles management and enhancement (by yaml and Javascript).</li>
      <li>Simple UI and supports custom theme color.</li>
      <li>Built-in support Clash.Meta core.</li>
      <li>System proxy setting and guard.</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
  
